This torrent contains the following 4 series - each fits onto a single DVD-R

A selection of nature films featuring David Attenborough (or in the case of Planet Earth narrated by him with a few spot appearances)

- 13 episodes

The Living Planet (1984) [DivX] [512x384] [350mb/ea] [~54min/ea]
- 12 episodes

The Private Life of Plants (1995) [DivX] [512x384] [350mb/ea] [~48min/ea]
- 6 episodes

Planet Earth (2006) [DivX] [464x256] [320MB/ea] [~59min/ea]
- 14 episodes (includes the 3 episodes of Planet Earth - The Future)

All are amazing and fascinating - Planet Earth in particular, if you can find it in Hi-Def then you should definitely buy it, as it was the first of its kind to be filmed in Hi-Def.
